Note:
aott/analysis/hotpath_analysis/execution_counter.runa
Execution Counter Module for AOTT Hot Path Detection

This module provides execution counting functionality for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Basic block execution counting
- Function call frequency tracking
- Loop iteration counting
- Branch taken frequency
- Method invocation profiling
- Edge execution frequency
- Instruction-level counting
- Sampling-based profiling
- Counter overflow handling
- Counter persistence and storage
- Multi-threaded counter management
- Counter aggregation and analysis
- Adaptive sampling rates
- Counter instrumentation insertion
- Performance impact minimization
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

